snippet.title: Childhood - PlayStation Talents 2018 Finalist (English)
snippet.description:
Childhood is a 3D narrative adventure with resource management, survival and stealth mechanics. 

PlayStation Talents 2018 Finalist. Trailer edited by Alberto Sanchez.
